Class TabbedImpl

  • java.lang.Object

  • public final class TabbedImpl
extends org.netbeans.core.windows.view.ui.tabcontrol.AbstractTabbedImpl
    The default Tabbed implementation. The actual visual tab container is TabContainer class and most of its logic is wired in Controller class.
